description: Full 'slot-in' planning application for phased residential led mixed-use development above and surrounding Nine Elms Station, comprising three new residential buildings of 21 storeys, 16 storeys and 17 storeys providing a total of 479 homes  (Use Class C3), plus small scale commercial floorspace of 108m2 (Expanded Use Classes A1-A4 and D1), works within the Nine Elms Station 'boxes', a new public square, and associated works.
